        <item>
            <title>华为 Pura 70 Ultra 修复 AI 除衫漏洞，禁止用户「一键脱衣」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/huawei-pura-70-ultra-ai-nake-bug-fixed/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-pura-70-ultra-ai-nake-bug-fixed</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/huawei-pura-70-ultra-ai-nake-bug-fixed/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 10:30:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[HUAWEI Pura 70 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231285</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-vmark="75bb"><span class="hot-topic" data-topic-logo="//pimg.ithome.com/products/2024/04/23/1253ab7f-fc49-448c-9d61-68529e7069b5.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" data-topic-id="36600">早前有网友发现，HUAWEI Pura 70 Ultra 手机内置的 AI 消除功能竟可「一键脱衣」，HUAWEI 日前已修复该漏洞，禁止用户这样使用 AI 。</span></p><p data-vmark="1bae">HUAWEI Pura 70 Ultra 手机图库设有 AI 消除功能。据中国媒体报道，有中国网民分享指，这个功能可以消除照片上女性胸口部分的衣服。网民在影片中示范，只要使用 AI 消除功能涂抹相片女生的胸部，女生胸口的衣服就会神奇地「消失」。</p><p data-vmark="1bae"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1231288 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/77ddea116c5043f0a064-262x580.png" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/77ddea116c5043f0a064-262x580.png 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/77ddea116c5043f0a064.png 407w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1231290 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/f9428216796140d4bf20-262x580.png" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/f9428216796140d4bf20-262x580.png 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/f9428216796140d4bf20.png 407w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="1bae">▲网民使用 HUAWEI 的 AI 功能，涂抹女性的胸部（图片来源：IT 之家）</p><p data-vmark="1bae"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231289" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ef4c8779b1f545d493d1-262x580.png" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ef4c8779b1f545d493d1-262x580.png 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ef4c8779b1f545d493d1.png 407w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="1bae">▲AI 随后自动生成内容（图片来源：IT 之家）</p><p data-vmark="1bae"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231290" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/f9428216796140d4bf20-262x580.png" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/f9428216796140d4bf20-262x580.png 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/f9428216796140d4bf20.png 407w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="1bae">▲AI 自动生成「事业线」（图片来源：IT 之家）</p><p data-vmark="4f54">示范可见，AI 功能能够按照相片涂抹区域生成相应画面。据中国媒体报道，有 HUAWEI 用家成功在自己的手机测试这项功能，引起网民热论。华为表示上述功能仅属漏洞，现时已经升级 AI 演算法解决该问题。《IT 之家》引述「看山的叔叔」微博指，HUAWEI 已经修复 Pura 70 Ultra 手机 AI 漏洞，现时用户再使用这个功能「脱衣」时会显示「此图无法使用消除功能」。</p><p data-vmark="1bae"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231293" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425165419-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425165419-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425165419.jpg 820w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="1bae">▲图片来源：IT 之家</p><p data-vmark="4f54">资料来源：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/763965.htm">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/15/huawei-pocket2-china-version-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Huawei Pocket 2 国行　外型，手感，体验，屏幕，相机，效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/02/huawei-matepadpro132-hk-version-reivew/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Huawei MatePad Pro 13.2 港行　外形　手感　键盘　星闪笔　屏幕　效能深入评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/25/huawei-freeclip-review/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Huawei FreeClip　外形　佩戴感　隔声效果　开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/huawei-pura-70-ultra-ai-nake-bug-fixed/mobile-phone/">华为 Pura 70 Ultra 修复 AI 除衫漏洞，禁止用户「一键脱衣」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
