        <item>
            <title>龙芯下一代处理器 8 核心 3.5 GHz   「近十年龙芯 CPU 单核性能提升 20 倍」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/loongson-8-core-35-ghz-cpu/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=loongson-8-core-35-ghz-cpu</link>
