            <title>微信支付：外国人也可用数字人民币，毋须证件+开设中国地区银行帐户</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/foreigner-can-use-wechat-pay/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=foreigner-can-use-wechat-pay</link>
