            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>微信支付宣布外国人可使用微信支付「数字人民币」，毋须提供个人资料。</p><p>微信设有多种「小程式」，支援在酒旅、餐饮、零售使用「数字人民币」，据《cnBeta》报道，中国人民银行先前发布的《境外来华人士数字人民币支付指南》，表示外籍人士去中国旅游后可注册帐号，按照说明开设「数字人民币」钱包，随即可以用「数字人民币」App 扫微信支付商业收款码与经营收款码支付。</p><p>《境外来华人士数字人民币支付指南》指，外籍人士可使用国际银行卡付款，如使用「数字人民币」匿名钱包，不需提供护照，亦无须亲自前往银行办理境内帐户。现时微信支付「数字人民币」可以使用逾 210 个国家手机号码注册。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150458-437x580.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150458-437x580.jpg 437w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150458.jpg 679w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 437px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231247" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150508-369x580.jpg" alt="" width="369" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150508-369x580.jpg 369w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150508.jpg 572w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 369px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150516-557x580.jpg" alt="" width="557" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150516-557x580.jpg 557w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150516.jpg 746w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 557px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150551-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150551-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150551.jp